== 宣传价值 ==
这场奥运会经常出现在朝鲜向联合国军士兵分发的[[心理战|心理战]]小册子和传单中。<ref>''Peace'' "magazine" (n.2), October 1952</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rememberingscotlandatwar.org.uk/Accessible/Image/GetImage/360/-/a96cb995-3a58-4e1e-b467-394802f6fa30.jpg |title=Propaganda leaflet, 1952 |accessdate=2016-03-04 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304115501/http://www.rememberingscotlandatwar.org.uk/Accessible/Image/GetImage/360/-/a96cb995-3a58-4e1e-b467-394802f6fa30.jpg |dead-url=yes }}</ref>1952年的战俘营奥运会使中国人民志愿军得以宣传投降者可享有的良好待遇。<ref name="kmike.com">{{Cite web|title=POW Olympics Intro RedirectPage|url=http://www.kmike.com/POW_Olympics/pow/POW_Olympics_Names.htm|publisher=}}</ref><ref>http://library.ndsu.edu/digital/files/2010/04/Themes-in-Korean-War.pdf{{Dead link|date=February 2019 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> 

